message.body: Hey. How is everything? How's Cassy?
Hey it's good. We're just getting to the restaurant
Oh wow. I thought you'd have been there already. Long day.
Can you believe that I just got a call from Pennsylvania hospital's nurse recruiter about an interview?
Are You serious? What are you gonna do?
Haha. I turned it down. It was part time and day night rotation for med surg.
But it makes me feel good knowing that the year mark really does make a difference.
Okay
Yeah
I'm almost at my parents. I have to interview some one and then I'll be there
Ok. In still trying get out of here.
Oh wow I thought you were home
Do you have work to do when you get home? I'm leaving now.
Not much
Ok. Did you want to watch a movie?
Yes actually I was gonna ask you
Haha. Ok.
Dinner will be done at 530. Hope you make it but we'll keep it warm if you don't. Santucci sandwiches. Home made.
Love you baby.
If you talk to Cassy about the beach Saturday is fine. I can't call out but you should go. I'd be more upset if they choose to go to the pool instead of the beach and I missed it. Haha.
